day 1 web server

********host multiple Domain on one Virtual server*******

learning objectives

1. setup and host multiple website on a single virtula server 

2. we will use AWS , but this ca be down with any cloude hosting provider 

3. doploy ubuntu  

4. install LAMP stack on server (Apache , mysql php )

5. install phpmyadmin





** (if you windowd then use putty )

6. configer virtual host on our server for each domain

7. manage name server on our domain registare admin palnal 

8. configer a dnas zone file on the route 53

9. configure SSl certificates for each domain we are hosting on our server using let's encriypt.

 
